# A donde.vamos.back VAlpha

[![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/license-MIT-blue.svg)](LICENSE)
[![Node.js Version](https://img.shields.io/badge/node-%3E%3D%2014.16-brightgreen)](https://nodejs.org/)
[![Express Version](https://img.shields.io/badge/express-%5E4.21.2-lightgrey)](https://expressjs.com/)

A donde vamos backed project to interact to Adondevamos.web project made by @MoysAkuma

## Features

- Site managment
- User managment
- Place managment
- Trip managment

## Prerequisites

- Node.js (version X.X or higher)
- npm (version X.X or higher)
- express (v4.21.2 or higher)
- @supabase/supabase-js (version 2.49.4 or higher)
- dotenv (version ^16.5.0)
- Body-parser (version 2.2.0 or higher)
- redis (version 5.8.3 or higher)
- connect-redis (version 9.0.0 or higher)
- cookie-parser (version 1.4.7 or higher)
- cors (version 2.8.5 or higher)
- express-session (version 1.18.2 or higher)
- whatwg-url (version 14.2.0 or higher)
- swagger-jsdoc (version 6.2.8 or higher)
- swagger-ui-express (version 14.2.0 or higher)


## Installation

1. Clone the repository:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/MoysAkuma/Adondevamosback
   cd adondevamosback

## EndPoints
    - /v1/login
	    A post method to auth and user, returns 409 if credentials are not valid.
     - /v1/check-auth
	    A get method to check if session is still valid
    - /v1/Logout
	    A post method to delete session of user
    - /v1/Countries
	    Post method to create a new country and get method retrieves last 5 created countries
    - /v1/Countries/:CountryID
	    Put method to update all information of a created country, Get retrieves a single record by Id, delete eliminates a record by ID.
    - /v1/Countries/:CountryID/Hide
	    A patch method to change value of hide to false
    - /v1/Countries/:CountryID/Show
	    A patch method to change value of hide to true
    - /v1/States
	    Post method create a new state, Get retrieves a list of 5 created place by creation date 
    - /v1/States/:StateID
	    Put method update all info of a state, Get retrieves a single state info by id, delete eliminate a record by id.
    - /v1/States/ByCountryID/:countryid
	    A get method to retrieves all states by countryid
    - /v1/Cities
	    Post method create a new city, Get retrieves a list of 5 created cities by creation date
    - /v1/Cities/:cityID
	    Put method update all info of a city by id, Get retrieves a single city info by id, delete eliminate a record by id.
    - /v1/Cities/ByState/:stateid
	    A get method to retrieves a list of cities by a state
    - /v1/Facilities
	    Get method retrieves a list of created facilities, Post create a new record of facilities.
    - /v1/Facilities/:facilityID
	    Put method update all info of a facility by id, Get retrieves a single facility info by id, delete eliminate a record by id.
    - /v1/Facilities/:facilityID/Hide
	    A patch method to hide a facility by id
    - /v1/Facilities/:facilityID/Show
	    A patch method to show a facility by id
    - /v1/Users/:UserID
    	Get method retrieves info of a user, Put updates info of a user by id, delete eliminate a record by id.
    - /v1/Users/Password/Change
	    A patch method to change password
    - /v1/Users/:UserID/Show
	    A patch method to show a user
    - /v1/Users/:UserID/Hide
	    A patch method to hide a user
    - /v1/Users/Search/tag=:searchText
	    A get method to search a list of users that matches name or description of a given text
    - /v1/Places
	    Get method retrieves a list of created places by creation date, Post method creates a new place.
    - /v1/Users/Verify/Email/:email
	    A get method to verify if an email is available in sistem
    - /v1/Places/Search/name=:PlaceName
	    A get method to search a list of places that matches name or description of a given text
    - /v1/Places/:PlaceID
	    Get method retrieves info of a created place by id, Put method update all info by id, delete eliminate a record that matches with id.
    - /v1/Places/:PlaceID/Facilities
	    Get method retrieves a list of facilities that placeid field matches of an id
    - /v1/View/Places/:PlaceID/Facilities
	A get method to search multiple info of a facility to show at system
    - /v1/Places/:PlaceID/Facilities/:FacilityID
	    TBD
    - /v1/Places/Ubications/:CountryID/:StateID/:CityID
	    A get method to get Country name, State name and city name by id
    - /v1/Trips
	    Get method retrieves a list of last created places by creation date, Post create a new trip.
    - /v1/Trips/:TripID
	    Get method retrieves info of a created trip by id, Put method update all info by id, delete eliminate a record that matches with id.
    - /v1/Trips/View/News
	    A gett method to retrieves a list of 5 last created trips
    - /v1/Trips/:TripID/Members
	    Get method retrieves all members that matches tripid field of members list, Put update all info of a list of members of a given id.
    - /v1/Trips/:TripID/Itinerary
	    Get method retrieves itinerary that matches tripid field of itineraries, Put update an itinerary of a given id.
    - /v1/Trips/Search
        post method to search by filters
    - /v1/Places/Search
        post method to search by filters